				<div class="content">
					<h2>BAHAR TEKSTİL SAN VE TİC A.Ş.</h2>
<p><strong>QUALITY, ENVIRONMENT, OCCUPATIONAL HEALTH AND SAFETY POLICY</strong><br />All employees within Bahar Tesktil adopt Quality, Environment, Occupational Health and Safety management systems as their main policy. Our employees are responsible for implementing, improving and providing necessary resources of these systems.<br /><strong><br />Our Quality Policy</strong><br />• Creating Bahar Tekstil “quality culture”,<br />• Setting quality standards within Bahar Tekstil,<br />• Providing necessary conditions to reach the highest performance,<br />• Focusing all our activities on customer satisfaction,<br />• Following today’s fashion and trends closely, presenting the best culture for customer expectations and developing new products.<br /><br /><strong>Our Environment Policy</strong><br />• Working respectively to the community and environment,<br />• Protecting global resources and providing energy efficiency,<br />• Ensuring the preventing of pollution, reducing of waste and disposing of waste primarily by recycling,<br />• Providing a safe and healthy working environment for all employees,<br /><strong>Within the frame of these policies;</strong><br />• Stimulating our suppliers and customers to join us on quality, environment, occupational health and safety areas which we always aim to improve,<br />• Increasing the satisfaction of our employees continuously,<br />• Improving of the quality of the products and services we provide to our customers consistently and therefore manufacturing products that meet the expectations of the customers and are in compliance with the regulation of the country which we sell them,<br />• Keeping updated, reviewing and improving our management system as to the internationally approved standards, is the main duty, sincere commitment of our company and employees.<br /><br /><strong>Ahmet Aysu<br />President of the board of directors</strong></p>				</div>
